        <div class="content">
          <p>Do mention your accomplishments and exampes of your successes.</p>
          <p>Don't forget to proofread for spelling mistakes.</p>
          <p>Do update yoru resume frequently and keep a copy readily available to present.</p>
          <p> Don't overload your resume, only add what presents the best YOU.</p> 
